shortForecast: Widespread Heavy Snow then Mostly Sunny
name: New Year's Day
detailedForecast: Widespread snow before 10am. Mostly sunny. High near 31, with temperatures falling to around 19 in the afternoon. West wind 9 to 14 mph, with gusts as high as 29 mph. Chance of precipitation is 100%. New snow accumulation of less than half an inch possible.
